casebody.data:
Mia Jane STEPHENS, General Administrator and Administrator ad Prosequendum of the Estate of Andre Henry, Deceased, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
48 BRANFORD PLACE ASSOCIATES, LLC, et al., Defendants,
and
Ramelle Massey, individually and as the servant, agent and employee of Massey Insurance Agency, Defendants-Respondents. C-925 September Term 2018
082451 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004858-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
